{
  "id": "nce4-l41",
  "title": "Lesson 41: Training Elephants",
  "audio": "/audio/nce4/41－Training Elephants.mp3",
  "image": "/images/coming-soon.jpg",
  "segments": [
    {
      "id": "intro_1",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "Lesson 41",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 0.6,
      "endTime": 2.74,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Lesson",
            "pos": "n.",
            "meaning": "课程，第...课"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_2",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "Training elephants",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 2.75,
      "endTime": 10.53
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_3",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "At what point does the training of a captive wild elephant begin?",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 10.54,
      "endTime": 17.73,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "At",
            "pos": "prep.",
            "meaning": "在...（小地点/时刻）"
          },
          {
            "word": "What",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "什么"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_4",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "Two main techniques have been used for training elephants, which we may call respectively the tough and the gentle.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 17.74,
      "endTime": 27.24,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s1",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "The former method simply consists of setting an elephant to work and beating him until he does what is expected of him.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 27.25,
      "endTime": 36.66,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "What",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "什么"
          },
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s2",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "Apart from any moral considerations this is a stupid method of training,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 36.67,
      "endTime": 42.28,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "This",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "这，这个"
          },
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s3",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "for it produces a resentful animal who at a later stage may well turn man-killer.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 42.29,
      "endTime": 49.3,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          },
          {
            "word": "At",
            "pos": "prep.",
            "meaning": "在...（小地点/时刻）"
          },
          {
            "word": "Well",
            "pos": "adj.",
            "meaning": "健康的，良好的"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s4",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "The gentle method requires more patience in the early stages,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 49.31,
      "endTime": 53.71
    },
    {
      "id": "s5",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "but produce a cheerful good-tempered elephant who will give many years of loyal service.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 53.72,
      "endTime": 61.85,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s6",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "The first essential in elephant training is to assign to the animal a single mahout who will be entirely responsible for the job.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 61.86,
      "endTime": 72.01,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s7",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "Elephants like to have one master just as dogs do, and are capable of a considerable degree of personal affection.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 72.02,
      "endTime": 81.7,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s8",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "There are even stories of half-trained elephant calves who have refused to feed and pined to death",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 81.71,
      "endTime": 90.53,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s9",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "when by some unavoidable circumstance they have been deprived of their own trainer.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 90.54,
      "endTime": 98.4,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s10",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "Such extreme cases must probably be taken with a grain of salt,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 98.41,
      "endTime": 103.25,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s11",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "but they do underline the general principle that the relationship between elephant and mahout is the key to successful training.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 103.26,
      "endTime": 114.23,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          },
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s12",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "The most economical age to capture an elephant for training is between 15 and 20 years,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 114.24,
      "endTime": 121.52,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s13",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "for it is then almost ready to undertake heavy work and can begin to earn its keep straight away.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 121.53,
      "endTime": 129.28,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          },
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s14",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "But animals of this age do not easily become subservient to man, and a very firm hand must be employed in the early stages.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 129.29,
      "endTime": 139.41,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "This",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "这，这个"
          },
          {
            "word": "Not",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "不，不是"
          },
          {
            "word": "Man",
            "pos": "n.",
            "meaning": "男人"
          },
          {
            "word": "Very",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "很，非常"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s15",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "The captive elephant, still roped to a tree,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 139.42,
      "endTime": 142.73
    },
    {
      "id": "s16",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "plunges and screams every time a man approaches, and for several days will probably refuse all food through anger and fear.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 142.74,
      "endTime": 154.26,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Man",
            "pos": "n.",
            "meaning": "男人"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s17",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "Sometimes a tame elephant is tethered nearby to give the wild one confidence,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 154.27,
      "endTime": 160.26,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s18",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "and in most cases the captive gradually quietens down and begins to accept its food.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 160.27,
      "endTime": 167.8,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s19",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "The next stage is to get the elephant to the training establishment,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 167.81,
      "endTime": 171.86,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s20",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "a ticklish business which is achieved with the aid of two tame elephants roped to the captive on either side.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 171.87,
      "endTime": 179.96,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s21",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "When several elephants are being trained at one time,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 179.97,
      "endTime": 184.04,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "At",
            "pos": "prep.",
            "meaning": "在...（小地点/时刻）"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s22",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "it is customary for the new arrival to be placed between the stalls of two captives whose training is already well advanced.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 184.05,
      "endTime": 193.87,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          },
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          },
          {
            "word": "Well",
            "pos": "adj.",
            "meaning": "健康的，良好的"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s23",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "It is then left completely undisturbed with plenty of food and water",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 193.88,
      "endTime": 199.14,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          },
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s24",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "so that it can absorb the atmosphere of its new home and see that nothing particularly alarming is happening to its companions.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 199.15,
      "endTime": 208.38,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          },
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          },
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s25",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "When it is eating normally, its own training begins.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 208.39,
      "endTime": 213.26,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          },
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s26",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "The trainer stands in front of the elephant holding a long stick with a sharp metal point.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 213.27,
      "endTime": 219.69
    },
    {
      "id": "s27",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "Two assistants, mounted on tame elephants, control the captive from either side,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 219.7,
      "endTime": 226.62
    },
    {
      "id": "s28",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "while others rub their hands over his skin to the accompaniment of a monotonous and soothing chant.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 226.63,
      "endTime": 235.05,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s29",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "This is supposed to induce pleasurable sensations in the elephant,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 235.06,
      "endTime": 239.72,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "This",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "这，这个"
          },
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s30",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "and its effects are reinforced by the use of endearing epithets,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 239.73,
      "endTime": 243.68,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s31",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "such as 'ho! my son', or 'ho! my father', or 'my mother', according to the age and sex of the captive.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 243.69,
      "endTime": 255.7,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "My",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "我的"
          },
          {
            "word": "Son",
            "pos": "n.",
            "meaning": "儿子"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s32",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "The elephant is not immediately susceptible to such blandishments, however, and usually lashes fiercely with its trunk in all directions.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 255.71,
      "endTime": 265.46,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          },
          {
            "word": "Not",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "不，不是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s33",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "These movements are controlled by the trainer with the metal-pointed stick,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 265.47,
      "endTime": 270,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s34",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "and the trunk eventually becomes so sore that the elephant curls it up and seldom afterwards uses it for offensive purposes.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 270.01,
      "endTime": 275.01,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          },
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          }
        ]
      }
    }
  ]
}
